text: Nicholas Kőszegi can refer to one of the many members of the Kőszegi family: * Nicholas I Kőszegi (fl. 1266–1299), Palatine of Hungary * Nicholas III Kőszegi (fl. 1308–1313), Master of the Treasury of Hungary * Nicholas Kőszegi (fl. 1308–1336), bishop of Győr * Nicholas II Kőszegi (fl. 1314–1332), Master of the Horse and ancestor of the Rohonci family Category:Hungarian people Category:History of Hungary
title: Nicholas Kőszegi
